SuperSimpleSpawners
===================

Spawners drop eggs (permission: sss.drop.*)

Eggs place spawners (permission: sss.place.*)

All of above (permission: sss.*)

EVEN OPS NEED THESE PERMISSIONS!

Specific create permissions
  sss.drop.entity_type
  sss.place.entity_type

entity_type needs to be the lowercase form of the names found here:
  http://jd.bukkit.org/apidocs/org/bukkit/entity/EntityType.html